<li id="cite_note-58"><b><a href="#cite_ref-58" title="">^</a></b> <i><a href="http://www.radiotheatre.org/enternarnia/press.html" class="external text" title="http://www.radiotheatre.org/enternarnia/press.html" rel="nofollow">Enter Narnia</a></i>, Focus on the Family Radio Theatre, 2005.</li>
<li id="cite_note-59"><b><a href="#cite_ref-59" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://blog.mlive.com/james_sanford/2008/12/disney_is_no_longer_under_the.html" class="external text" title="http://blog.mlive.com/james_sanford/2008/12/disney_is_no_longer_under_the.html" rel="nofollow">"Disney No Longer Under Spell of Narnia"</a>. December 2008<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://blog.mlive.com/james_sanford/2008/12/disney_is_no_longer_under_the.html" class="external free" title="http://blog.mlive.com/james_sanford/2008/12/disney_is_no_longer_under_the.html" rel="nofollow">http://blog.mlive.com/james_sanford/2008/12/disney_is_no_longer_under_the.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Disney+No+Longer+Under+Spell+of+Narnia&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=December+2008&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.mlive.com%2Fjames_sanford%2F2008%2F12%2Fdisney_is_no_longer_under_the.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Chronicles_of_Narnia"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ol>
